---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/layout/Header.astro";
---

<Layout title="La Solución - Familias Palmete">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="solution-hero">
      <div class="solution-hero-content">
        <span class="section-label">LA SOLUCIÓN</span>
        <h2>La organización<br /><span class="highlight">colectiva es la clave</span></h2>
        <p class="hero-description">
          Tres pasos para conseguir tu alquiler de 200€. <strong>Ya lo logramos en Palmete.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="roadmap-section">
      <div class="roadmap-container">

        <div class="roadmap-item" data-aos="fade-right">
          <div class="step-number">01</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Infomación</h3>
            <p>Conoce tus derechos como inquilino de VPO y las vías legales para defenderlos. Te asesoramos sin coste.</p>
            <div class="step-icon">📚</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="roadmap-item" data-aos="fade-left">
          <div class="step-number">02</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Organización</h3>
            <p>Únete con otros vecinos en un sindicato de inquilinos. La fuerza es colectiva, no luches solo.</p>
            <div class="step-icon">👥</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="roadmap-item" data-aos="fade-right">
          <div class="step-number">03</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Acción</h3>
            <p>Juntos paramos desahucios y negociamos alquileres justos. La unión hace la fuerza.</p>
            <div class="step-icon">✊</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      <div class="result-as-step-wrapper" data-aos="fade-left">
        <div class="step-number">04</div>
        <div class="result-story" data-aos="zoom-in">
          <div class="result-story-content">
            <div class="result-stats">
              <div class="result-number">200€</div>
              <div class="result-text">alquiler mensual<br />por piso VPO</div>
              <div class="result-badge">TODO VÍA LEGAL, SIN OKUPAS</div>
            </div>

            <div class="step-icon-topright">🏆</div>

          <div class="result-details">
            <h3>Lo conseguimos en <span>Palmete, Sevilla.</span></h3>
            <p>
              <strong>11 familias unidas y asesoradas por las organizaciones</strong>, han frenado un intento de desahucio ilegal y <strong>han conseguido alquileres</strong> simbólicos <strong>de 200€</strong> en viviendas VPO.
            </p>

            <p>
              Ubicadas en la calle Verdad nº54, estas familias tomaron la iniciativa de trabajar juntas y buscar asesoramiento profesional para defender sus derechos. Gracias a su esfuerzo personal, la colaboración entre vecinos y el diálogo con las instituciones locales, el Ayuntamiento de Sevilla encontró una solución: mantener sus hogares en régimen de vivienda protegida, con las reparaciones incluidas. Un ejemplo de cómo el compromiso individual y la unión vecinal logran resultados reales.
            </p>

            <div class="story-visual">
              <img
                src="/images/victory.png"
                alt="Personas levantando pancarta"
                class="story-image"
              />
            </div>

            <p class="articles-label">Así lo contaron los medios:</p>

            <div class="article-badges">
              <a
                href="https://www.eldiario.es/sevilla/chupan-sangre-protesta-arropa-sevilla-11-familias-expulsadas-vpo-comprarlas-banco_1_12988074.html"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="article-badge"
              >
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M19 20H5C3.89543 20 3 19.1046 3 18V6C3 4.89543 3.89543 4 5 4H19C20.1046 4 21 4.89543 21 6V18C21 19.1046 20.1046 20 19 20Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"></path>
                  <path d="M7 8H17M7 12H17M7 16H13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>El Diario de Sevilla</span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.lavozdelsur.es/ediciones/sevilla/indignacion-desahucio-en-sevilla-11-familias-con-menores-cargo-en-bloque-propiedad-santander_349389_102.html"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="article-badge"
              >
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M19 20H5C3.89543 20 3 19.1046 3 18V6C3 4.89543 3.89543 4 5 4H19C20.1046 4 21 4.89543 21 6V18C21 19.1046 20.1046 20 19 20Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"></path>
                  <path d="M7 8H17M7 12H17M7 16H13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>La Voz del Sur</span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.101tv.es/la-solidaridad-obrera-frena-la-entrada-de-los-especuladores-en-palmete-el-banco-se-va-las-familias-se-quedan/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="article-badge"
              >
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M19 20H5C3.89543 20 3 19.1046 3 18V6C3 4.89543 3.89543 4 5 4H19C20.1046 4 21 4.89543 21 6V18C21 19.1046 20.1046 20 19 20Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"></path>
                  <path d="M7 8H17M7 12H17M7 16H13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>101TV</span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://izquierdarevolucionaria.net/index.php/estado-espanol/general/15008-victoria-de-la-lucha-vecinal-contra-los-desahucios-en-palmete-sevilla"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="article-badge"
              >
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M19 20H5C3.89543 20 3 19.1046 3 18V6C3 4.89543 3.89543 4 5 4H19C20.1046 4 21 4.89543 21 6V18C21 19.1046 20.1046 20 19 20Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"></path>
                  <path d="M7 8H17M7 12H17M7 16H13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>IR</span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://barrioshartos.org/erase-una-vez-en-san-jose-de-palmete/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="article-badge"
              >
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M19 20H5C3.89543 20 3 19.1046 3 18V6C3 4.89543 3.89543 4 5 4H19C20.1046 4 21 4.89543 21 6V18C21 19.1046 20.1046 20 19 20Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"></path>
                  <path d="M7 8H17M7 12H17M7 16H13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Barrios Hartos</span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://sevilla.cnt.es/2026/02/la-lucha-obrera-echa-al-santander-de-la-verdad/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="article-badge"
              >
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M19 20H5C3.89543 20 3 19.1046 3 18V6C3 4.89543 3.89543 4 5 4H19C20.1046 4 21 4.89543 21 6V18C21 19.1046 20.1046 20 19 20Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"></path>
                  <path d="M7 8H17M7 12H17M7 16H13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>CNT Sevilla</span>
              </a>
            </div>

            <p class="videos-label">Mira el proceso en video:</p>

            <div class="video-badges">
              <a
                href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wmGADykbbBc"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="video-badge"
              >
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M8 5V19L19 12L8 5Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Situación previa</span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BbBBH6ixPFg"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="video-badge"
              >
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M8 5V19L19 12L8 5Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Quejas y organización</span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iqAX6a_0PgI"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="video-badge"
              >
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M8 5V19L19 12L8 5Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>La manifestación</span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.youtube.com/shorts/Fxe_K3l3FDU"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="video-badge"
              >
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M8 5V19L19 12L8 5Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>La victoria (Short)</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>¿Quieres el mismo resultado?</h2>
        <p>Únete al mapa de alquileres y comienza tu lucha legal.</p>
        <a href="/mapa" class="cta-button">
          IR AL MAPA
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M5 12H19M19 12L12 5M19 12L12 19" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .solution-hero {
    width: 100%;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 10rem 2rem 6rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .solution-hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .solution-hero h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #111;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .roadmap-section {
    width: 100%;
    background: #0a1929;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .roadmap-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 0;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .roadmap-container::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--color-accent), transparent);
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .roadmap-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .result-as-step-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .result-as-step-wrapper .step-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .result-as-step-wrapper .result-story {
    flex:1 1 0;
    margin:0;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .result-as-step .result-story-content {
    width:100%;
  }

  .roadmap-item:nth-child(odd) {
    flex-direction: row;
  }

  .roadmap-item:nth-child(even) {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .step-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-content {
    background: #0a1929;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    flex: 1;
    transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-content:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .step-content p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .step-icon {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .result-story {
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .result-story-content {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap:2rem;
    background: #0a1929;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 3rem;
  }

  .result-stats {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .result-stats .step-number {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .step-icon-topright {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .result-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 4.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .result-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .result-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .result-details h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .result-details h3 span {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .result-details p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-visual {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .story-image {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 12px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .articles-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .article-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .article-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .article-badge:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .article-badge svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .videos-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .video-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .video-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .video-badge:hover {
    background: #ff0000;
    color: #fff;
    border-color: #ff0000;
  }

  .video-badge svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .result-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 4.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .result-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .result-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .cta-section {
    width: 100%;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .cta-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #111;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #ffffff;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: none;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 140ms ease, box-shadow 140ms ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.3);
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .solution-hero {
      padding: 8rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    }

    .roadmap-item {
      flex-direction: column !important;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .result-as-step {
      flex-direction: column !important;
    }

    .result-as-step .result-story {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .step-number {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .step-icon {
      position: relative;
      top: auto;
      right: auto;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .result-number {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .result-story {
      max-width:100%;
    }

    .result-as-step-wrapper {
      flex-direction: column !important;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .result-as-step-wrapper .step-number {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .result-as-step-wrapper .result-story {
      width:100%;
    }

    .result-story-content {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .result-details h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .article-badges,
    .video-badges {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
